</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">Hololive英语-Promise-订阅人数首次突破100万</h3><p>无名无名所属的 Hololive English 的《Promise》（原 Council &amp; Project:HOPE）以艺人频道的订阅人数在出道后立即大幅减少的现象而闻名，《九十九草无名》也是如此。除了先生毕业之外，公司也面临着困难，一些其他公司和团体的人才表示， <em>“理事会的表现没有达到他们的预期</em>。” </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="GUIUrVqqa7"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-hololive-english-youtube-subscribers-of-5-new-talents-decreased-but-the-cause-is-unknown/">VTuber集团Hololive英语频道5名新人订阅人数减少，原因不明</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber团体Hololive English的5位新人订阅人数减少，原因不明” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-hololive-english-youtube-subscribers-of-5-new-talents-decreased-but-the-cause-is-unknown/embed/#?secret=jHWkVZFvaq#?secret=GUIUrVqqa7" data-secret="GUIUrVqqa7" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="DmKLnZy977"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/the-line-of-sight-to-hololive-production-can-be-seen-from-the-interesting-exchanges-of-nijisanji-group-nijisanji-en-discord/">着眼于 Hololive Production 关于 Nijisanji “NIJISANJI EN” 的有趣交流 Discord</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“看 Hololive 制作：关于 Nijisanji “NIJISANJI EN”Discord 的有趣交流” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/the-line-of-sight-to-hololive-production-can-be-seen-from-the-interesting-exchanges-of-nijisanji-group-nijisanji-en-discord/embed/#?secret=4bTCjLrV6V#?secret=DmKLnZy977" data-secret="DmKLnZy977" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="kc0xoec583"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-tsukumo-sana-will-graduate-from-hololive-english-on-july-31-2022/">VTuber九十九草美琴于7月31日从hololive英语毕业</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Kujukusa Mikoto 将于 7 月 31 日从 Hololive English 毕业” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-tsukumo-sana-will-graduate-from-hololive-english-on-july-31-2022/embed/#?secret=RSjY1q51oW#?secret=kc0xoec583" data-secret="kc0xoec583" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p>所以，这一次，如果无名无名成为《无极》频道订阅人数突破100万的第一人，就会有一条Holo信息，上面写着：“即使你面临厄运，如果你继续踏踏实实做事，你也能获得成功。”一定能够实现这个里程碑。”不仅再次证明了现场制作的实力，对于刚出道就订阅人数大幅下降的hololive DEV_IS《ReGLOSS》来说也是令人鼓舞的，对于全世界所有目前正面临困境的VTuber人才来说，这或许是真的。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Lwfcwue8Xd"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-promise-birth-council-and-irys-join/">Hololive English -Promise- 诞生，是理事会和 IRyS 的一个新单位</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Hololive English -承诺 - 理事会和 IRyS 成立新单位” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-promise-birth-council-and-irys-join/embed/#?secret=VE241VtaIt#?secret=Lwfcwue8Xd" data-secret="Lwfcwue8Xd" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="3FsrTcL5kz"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-hakui-koyori-to-hold-singing-marathon-streaming