</style><p>以下文章详细介绍了“PhaseKALEiDO”五名成员的信息。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="yPvlhEVxxi"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/phase-connect-officially-announced-5-new-vtuber-phasekaleido-for-japan/">Phase Connect 正式宣布日本 5 名新 VTuber“PhaseKALEiDO”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Phase Connect 正式宣布日本 5 名新 VTuber“PhaseKALEiDO”” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/phase-connect-officially-announced-5-new-vtuber-phasekaleido-for-japan/embed/#?secret=pNcOcd9AIe#?secret=yPvlhEVxxi" data-secret="yPvlhEVxxi" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p> Phase Connect 是 Phase Connect LTD. 于 2021 年 6 月 18 日在加拿大温哥华设立的 VTuber 办事处。除了拥有包括初代成员Pipkin Pippa在内的一大批有影响力的艺人外，2023年（令和5年），附属艺人的同时观看人数（同时观看人数）预计将大幅增加随着它取得了巨大的进步，包括被录制，它不仅在英语国家而且在日本也逐渐被认可。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://twitter.com/PhaseConnectJP/status/1750284482182266940?t=tlilJ-WUXmAG9_b-7tji6Q&amp;s=19 </div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="6DaU9isHSc"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-phase-connect-advertising-at-shibuya-scramble-crossing/">Phase Connect进军日本涩谷Scramble Crossing广告新VTuber“PhaseKALEiDO”首次亮相</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Phase Connect 进军日本 涩谷 Scramble Crossing 广告新 VTuber“PhaseKALEiDO”首次亮相” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-phase-connect-advertising-at-shibuya-scramble-crossing/embed/#?secret=tRl3oBkowo#?secret=6DaU9isHSc" data-secret="6DaU9isHSc" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://phase-connect.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">相连接</a></p><cite>相连接有限公司</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="ZxVCgWIgGs"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/phase-connect-released-new-vtuber-phasekaleido-original-animation/">Phase Connect发布新VTuber“PhaseKALEiDO”原创动画</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Phase Connect 发布新VTuber“PhaseKALEiDO”原创动画” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/phase-connect-released-new-vtuber-phasekaleido-original-animation/embed/#?secret=11NbP4qCzV#?secret=ZxVCgWIgGs" data-secret="ZxVCgWIgGs" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p><a href="https://p2y.jp/phase-connect-released-new-vtuber-phasekaleido-original-animation/">新VTuber“PhaseKALEiDO”发布的Phase Connect原创动画</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/phase-connect-released-new-vtuber-phasekaleido-original-animation/feed/ 0 112798
